因此國民黨與國軍視為敵人，所以聲稱國民黨與國軍其實通共<br />\n<br />\n第六招：以香港人唔係華人，否定係中華民族，用以割裂抗戰歷史係別國他人民族歷史，一切苦難榮光同自己無關<br />\n<br />\n口黎去去，屈五毛黨就係如此六招橫行雙登，邊個唔合意影響佢地媚日反共立場，而又無辦法理直氣壯阻止他人出post，即用此六大法滅聲，消除異己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪on9架"},{"pid":"6a3687af6ebaf8b2e7c133a93a4eb286d87f05df","tid":265652,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T20:27:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"852286eb1de7bac69a4a2fed73f8f642372ddabb","tid":265652,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T20:39:25.000Z","msg":"嘩不得了呀"},{"pid":"e8f83f3da39406c3bc7ae6db41f11dd833a9b13d","tid":265652,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T20:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友嘩嘩嘩成條弱智咁</blockquote><br />\n好明顯係大陸仔黎  無第句"},{"pid":"06c1eedf0519af89ed11aa5649f98cbd16c03e2a","tid":265652,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T20:40:46.000Z","msg":"係咁嘩嘩嘩條傻柒 好似深山野人咁乜柒都未見到 就當樣樣野都驚世大發現"},{"pid":"a124e8a6dded63a6206938e97a65a0981d3f7745","tid":265652,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T21:02:33.000Z","msg":"未見過大蛇痾尿"},{"pid":"0ff5f25cf9a12cdce6cd4ce2e43dbf72a5b50dfd","tid":265652,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:33:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔車死佢？"},{"pid":"ababf5b16a78c6fbbfd03f5603b99b6a43564a20","tid":265652,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:36:59.000Z","msg":"哇  ~~~~ 嘩 ~~~~ 痴線 ~~~~ 哇 ~~~  嘩 ~~~~ 好勁喎 ~~~~ 嘩 ~~~~ 好大條呀 ~~~~ 射左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917040d7a3d45fa827c31bec666986dbc7fc2496","tid":265652,"uid":26106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔車死佢？</blockquote><br />\n點解要車死佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces