，個d狗次次出手都中呢六招之一，來來去去，非常容易識別</blockquote><br />\n扮民國五毛你都唔係第一個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ae435fa74a3a003cfe12ba4483056f8b045d50","tid":265652,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:41:12.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港都有呢d奇珍異獸"},{"pid":"2ae954731eba9c04e8533e82c01ae502462f4153","tid":265652,"uid":20455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:43:05.000Z","msg":"未見過大蛇痾尿咩"},{"pid":"adc3525fada73eb873e2d9227b78a2e9509cd407","tid":265652,"uid":32786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:47:52.000Z","msg":"其實朝早/ 中午一樣有<br />\n上次同女朋友粉嶺上蝴蝶山 去嘉道理條路 (北大刀刃附近咁行行下 <br />\n都係去林村算 太多樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁去林村條路好明顯冇乜人行過<br />\n地下成地樹葉(石屎路+泥路)<br />\n行到咁上下 聽到D聲 望上樹 就有好撚大條青竹蛇係樹上面<br />\n再行多陣 好撚大條蟒蛇 霸左條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見佢冇郁 即過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地都唔知點解咁大膽<br />\n跟住追到前面兩公婆 佢地話 見過幾次 頭先都見到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea40a14580c099c19ce07caae8359a424d41db55","tid":265652,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如一齊捉咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔好咁黐線啦 <br />\n先唔好講佢咁撚大條  有毒你都仆左街喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c54afc52ba9b7939e13a10376089097e0371c1","tid":265652,"uid":23187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前係youtube睇過全世界最巨型既蟒蛇，膽